What this API will be able to do

Social Media Applications

User -> Posts
1 to many

-Retrieve all users -- GET /Users
-Create a User -- POST /Users
-Retrieve one user -- GET /Users/Jon
-delete a user -- DELETE /Users/Jon

-Retrieve all posts for a User -- GET /Users/{id}/Posts
-Create a posts for a user -- POST /Users/{id}/Posts
-Retrieve details of a post -- GET /Users/{id}/Posts/{post_id}

spring boot looks at all classes and jars that are available in the class path and then trys to auto configure them
spring boot also converts beans to json and json to beans automatically from the auto configuration
error messaging also created by auto configure

dispatcher servlet handles all of the requests (url goes to dispatcher servlet)
dispatcher servlet knows all the different mappings created in project